tech.mcprison.prison.internal.inventory

Interface Inventory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<ItemStack>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AnvilInventory, BrewerInventory, CraftingInventory, EnchantingInventory, PlayerInventory

    public interface Inventory
extends java.lang.Iterable<ItemStack>
    Represents an inventory. An inventory can belong to a player, a chest, or to nothing at all (i.e. as a GUI).
